heading: ElDewrito 0.5.0 Released
body:
The team is proud to announce version 0.5.0 has been released. This update will allow you to play on all of the new maps present in the latest official release of Halo Online: High Ground, Last Resort, Narrows, Standoff, The Pit and Sandtrap.

For more information, please view the Official Reddit Thread

- ElDewrito Team
author: ED Team
